data.description: Priced to sell ! Military Relocation . New kitchen appliances 2021 and tankless water heater 2022. HVAC 2017 . Assumable VA loan 2.25 % .This charming four-bedroom, two-bathroom home is move-in ready and offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience.    Step inside to discover a well-designed layout, ideal for family living or a flexible home office setup. The two bathrooms are both stylish and functional, ensuring a comfortable daily routine.    One of the property's standout features is the low maintenance backyard, adorned with various fruit trees. Enjoy your own private oasis, surrounded by the beauty of nature and the bounty of fresh produce from citrus to apricot trees.    With Rio Vista's sunny climate and a welcoming community, this home provides not just a living space but a delightful lifestyle. Embrace the warmth and charm of 451 Gordon Street, where your dream of a comfortable, move-in-ready home in sunny Rio Vista becomes a reality.
